# Schema-validated ScoreRow JSONL files emitted by head_to_head.py and
# the differential runners. Raw stdout transcripts and per-run derived
# files (charts, summaries) are ignored — only the JSONL is committed
# when a run is part of a published headline.
#
# Convention:
#   <ISO8601>_<case_id>.jsonl    — committed when part of a headline run
#   <ISO8601>_<case_id>.stdout   — never committed
#   *.tmp / *.partial            — never committed
#
# To commit a run intentionally:
#   git add -f runs/<file>.jsonl
*.stdout
*.tmp
*.partial
.tmp_*
